title: Smart Target 2.0
detail: Much cool. Many target. Very better. Wow!
extended_details: Based on last year's Smart Target. We bring all the functionality of the last iteration, but less buggy, and with a game play aspect. Now, not only can you track your archery progress, but you can battle your friends in a physical and virtual archery game to the death!
